      "body" : " I have observed this bug overflowing the ping time calculations in the real network. \r\n\r\n     {\r\n        \"id\": 12,\r\n        ...\r\n        \"pingtime\": 0,\r\n        \"minping\": 9223372036854.775,\r\n        ...\r\n        \"synced_headers\": 379993,\r\n        \"synced_blocks\": 379993,\r\n      }\r\n\r\nAlternatively Bitcoin Core could use one of the monotonic clocks for the time deltas. ",
